{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0001","text":"從未聯想這年會變富翁 從未期望做夢一天可上太空","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":22},"semantics":{"themes":["平凡生活","對未來的想像"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["富翁","太空","聯想","期望"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,0,9,5,0,4,4,3,0,2,0,2,2,2,3,3,9,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cung4","mei6","lyun4","soeng2","ze5","nin4","bin3","fu3","jung1","cung4","mei6","kei4","mong6","zou6","mung6","jat1","tin1","ho2","taai3","hung1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"從未","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"聯想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這年","pos":"DET"},{"text":"會變","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"富翁","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"從未","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"期望","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"做夢","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"一天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"可","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"上","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"太空","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"此句使用兩個「從未」開頭，強調對過去的否定與對未來的想像，語氣平淡。"},"source":{"title":"愛妻號","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1215","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0002","text":"我續我窮言行無出衆 也像無用萬大事輕鬆","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["自我認知","生活態度"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["窮","出衆","無用","輕鬆"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,5,0,0,0,0,3,4,5,2,0,2,2,2,2,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","zuk6","ngo5","kung4","jin4","hang4","mou4","ceot1","zung3","jaa5","zoeng6","mou4","jung6","maan6","daai6","si6","hing1","sung1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我續","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"窮","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"言行","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"無","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"出衆","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"也","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"像","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"無用","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"萬","pos":"NUM"},{"text":"大事","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"輕鬆","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「我續我窮」為一種自嘲的表達，後半句「也像無用萬大事輕鬆」形成對比，展現一種豁達的生活態度。"},"source":{"title":"愛妻號","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1215","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0003","text":"但我夢想洗衣店有我這店東 營業如做運動靜靜跟你抱擁","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":24},"semantics":{"themes":["平凡夢想","愛情","溫馨生活"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["夢想","洗衣店","店東","抱擁"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,2,9,9,3,4,5,5,5,4,3,0,2,0,2,2,2,2,2,3,5,5,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","ngo5","mung6","soeng2","sai2","ji1","dim3","jau5","ngo5","ze5","dim3","dung1","jing4","jip6","jyu4","zou6","wan6","dung6","zing6","zing6","gan1","nei5","pou5","jung2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"夢想","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"洗衣店","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"店東","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"營業","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"做","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"運動","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"靜靜","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"跟","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"抱","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"擁","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「但」字轉折，引出平凡卻溫馨的夢想，將「營業」與「運動」類比，最後以「靜靜跟你抱擁」作結，情感溫暖。"},"source":{"title":"愛妻號","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1215","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0004","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0004","text":"我用笑容來援和粗重 你用甜蜜混合幸福來附送","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["付出","愛情","幸福"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["笑容","甜蜜","幸福","附送"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,4,0,0,0,0,3,5,2,0,2,2,2,2,3,0,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","jung6","siu3","jung4","loi4","wun4","wo4","cou1","nei5","jung6","tim4","mat6","wan6","hap6","hang6","fuk1","loi4","fu6","sung3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我用","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"笑容","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"來援","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"和","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"粗重","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"用","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"甜蜜","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"混合","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"幸福","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"來","pos":"PART"},{"text":"附送","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"運用「來援」和「混合」等動詞，將「笑容」與「甜蜜」具象化，描繪出付出與接收幸福的互動。"},"source":{"title":"愛妻號","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1215","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0005","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0005","text":"我 我愛你有如洗熨 我要漂白你失望 排除骯髒","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":19},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","關懷","淨化"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["洗熨","失望","排除","骯髒"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,4,5,5,0,9,2,5,4,3,2,5,3,2,0,0,3,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","ngo5","oi3","nei5","jau5","jyu4","sai2","wan6","ngo5","jiu3","piu1","baak6","nei5","sat1","mong6","paai4","ceoi4","ong1","zong1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"我愛你","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"有如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"洗熨","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我要","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"漂白","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"失望","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"排除","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"骯髒","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"以「洗熨」比喻對愛情的投入，並將「失望」和「骯髒」視為需要被「漂白」和「排除」的負面情緒，表達強烈的關懷與淨化意願。"},"source":{"title":"愛妻號","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1215","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0006","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0006","text":"無泡狀況 柔順似白雪飄降","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["純潔","美好","愛情"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["無泡","柔順","白雪","飄降"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,3,2,4,0,2,5,2,4,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mou4","paau1","zong6","fong3","jau4","seon6","ci5","baak6","syut3","piu1","gong3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"無泡","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"狀況","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"柔順","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"似","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"白雪","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"飄降","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「無泡狀況」延續洗衣的比喻，形容愛情的純淨無瑕，並以「柔順似白雪飄降」描繪出美好、輕柔的意境。"},"source":{"title":"愛妻號","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1215","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0007","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0007","text":"我愛你有如洗熨 你每次遇上風浪 仍然乾爽","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","保護","堅韌"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["洗熨","風浪","乾爽","遇上"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,4,5,5,0,9,2,5,5,4,2,3,2,0,0,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","oi3","nei5","jau5","jyu4","sai2","wan6","nei5","mui5","ci3","jyu6","fung1","long6","jing4","jin4","gon1","song2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我愛你","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"有如","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"洗熨","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"每次","pos":"DET"},{"text":"遇上","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"風浪","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"仍然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"乾爽","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"再次使用「洗熨」的比喻，強調愛情能使對方在面對困難（風浪）時，依然保持「乾爽」，展現保護與堅韌的力量。"},"source":{"title":"愛妻號","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1215","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0008","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0008","text":"人腦運作 程序會令你開朗","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":11},"semantics":{"themes":["影響","快樂","愛情"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["人腦","程序","開朗","令"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,2,4,0,2,2,5,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jan4","nou5","wan6","zok3","cing4","zeoi6","ling6","nei5","hoi1","long5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"人腦","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"運作","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"程序","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"會令","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"開朗","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"將愛情的影響比喻為「人腦運作」的「程序」，能使對方「開朗」，帶有積極正面的影響力。"},"source":{"title":"愛妻號","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1215","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0009","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0009","text":"在我夢想洗衣店顧客愛到訪 人疊人像滑浪就是因你發光","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":24},"semantics":{"themes":["事業成功","愛情","動力"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["夢想","洗衣店","顧客","發光"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,2,9,9,3,4,4,4,4,4,9,0,2,0,2,2,2,2,2,3,5,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoi6","ngo5","mung6","soeng2","sai2","ji1","dim3","gu3","haak3","oi3","dou3","fong2","jan4","dip6","jan4","zoeng6","waat6","long6","zau6","si6","jan1","nei5","faat3","gwong1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"夢想","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"洗衣店","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"顧客","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"到訪","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"人疊人","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"像","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"滑浪","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"就是","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"因","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"發光","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"將「顧客愛到訪」和「人疊人」形容為「滑浪」，生動地描繪事業的成功景象，並點明這是「因你發光」，將成功歸因於愛人。"},"source":{"title":"愛妻號","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1215","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0010","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0010","text":"我爲你狂繁忙和苦幹 你用凝望混合電波來又往","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["付出","愛情","回應"],"sentiment":"VERY_POSITIVE","keywords":["狂","繁忙","苦幹","凝望","電波"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,0,0,0,0,9,4,5,2,0,2,2,2,2,3,0,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","nei5","kwong4","faan4","mong4","wo4","fu2","gon3","nei5","jung6","jing4","mong6","wan6","hap6","din6","bo1","loi4","jau6","wong5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"爲","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"狂","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"繁忙","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"和","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"苦幹","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"用","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"凝望","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"混合","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"電波","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"來","pos":"PART"},{"text":"又","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"往","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「我為你狂繁忙和苦幹」表達為愛付出的努力，而「你用凝望混合電波來又往」則描繪了對方以溫柔的眼神和無形的聯繫作為回應，形成愛的互動。"},"source":{"title":"愛妻號","artists":["陳小春"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1215","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5bCP5pil_MTIxNQ_0009","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
